FBIS4-60320 "drnes100_j_94039" FBIS-NES-94-100 Daily Report 23 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Aden Defense Ministry Denies Attack Aden Defense Ministry Denies Attack EA2405084094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio in Arabic 2045 GMT 23 May 94 EA2405084094 Aden Democratic Republic of Yemen Radio Arabic BFN [Text] The Defense Ministry has stated that in order to justify its criminal action of directing missiles on Aden, which killed tens of women, children, and old men, the al-Ahmar gang media have announced that a missile was fired on Sanaa this evening. The Defense Ministry in the Democratic Republic of Yemen [DRY] categorically denies responsibility for this act.
